<subSubSection id="C36165495E31FF919E85FE09FC7D9A37" pageId="8" pageNumber="109" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BC436C25E31FF919E85FE09FC7D9A37" blockId="8.[166,1225,406,529]" pageId="8" pageNumber="109">
Species of the subfamily 
<taxonomicName id="4C7B4D415E31FF919C5FFE09FD4C9997" authorityName="Navas" authorityYear="1910" box="[513,702,406,433]" pageId="8" pageNumber="109" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Nothochrysinae">Nothochrysinae</taxonomicName>
are represented in all continents (excluding 
<collectingCountry id="F36C76525E31FF919EF8FE29FED699F7" box="[166,292,438,465]" name="Antarctica" pageId="8" pageNumber="109">Antarctica</collectingCountry>
) by seven genera (17 species). Only three species (
<taxonomicName id="4C7B4D415E31FF919D84FE29FE8C99D7" authority="Burgmeister, 1839" authorityName="Burgmeister" authorityYear="1839" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" genus="Hypochrysa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="109" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="elegans">
<emphasis id="B90FEAD05E31FF919D84FE29FB3B99F6" box="[986,1225,438,464]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="109">Hypochrysa elegans</emphasis>
Burgmeister, 1839
</taxonomicName>
; 
<taxonomicName id="4C7B4D415E31FF919FD6FE49FCC599D7" authority="Fabricius, 1793" authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1793" box="[392,823,470,497]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" genus="Nothochrysa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="109" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="capitata">
<emphasis id="B90FEAD05E31FF919FD6FE49FD8C99D6" box="[392,638,470,496]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="109">Nothochrysa capitata</emphasis>
Fabricius, 1793
</taxonomicName>
; and 
<taxonomicName id="4C7B4D415E31FF919D2CFE49FF129A37" authority="Stephens, 1836" authorityName="Stephens" authorityYear="1836" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" genus="Notochrysa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="109" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fulvipes">
<emphasis id="B90FEAD05E31FF919D2CFE49FBA199D6" box="[882,1107,470,496]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="109">Notochrysa fulvipes</emphasis>
Stephens, 1836
</taxonomicName>
) occur in Europe, including 
<collectingCountry id="F36C76525E31FF919C6FFE69FD639A37" box="[561,657,502,529]" name="Ukraine" pageId="8" pageNumber="109">Ukraine</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFEA4B335E31FF919CFEFE69FC719A37" author="Aspock, U." box="[672,899,502,529]" pageId="8" pageNumber="109" pagination="451 - 456" refId="ref6252" refString="Aspock, U. 1993. Geklartes und Ungeklartes im System der Neuroptera (Insecta: Holometabola). Mitteilungen der Deutschen Gesellschaft fur Allgemeine und Angewandte Entomologie, 8, 451 - 456." type="journal article" year="1993">Aspöck et al., 1993</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
